It would be nice if \{viewfile} macro can handle large fonts. Currently, different lines of text overlaps slightly among each other as shown in the following screenshot:

!LargeFont.jpg!

h5. Workaround:
# Go to Dashboard > Administration > Look and Feel > Custom HTML
# Paste the following code in the "At end of the HEAD" section:
{code}
<style>
/*This is for Word Doc*/
.office-document p span 
{
 line-height: 100%;
}
/*This is for Excel files*/
.office-document #panel1 table tbody tr td
{
 line-height: 100%;
}
</style>
{code}
# Save the Custom HTML

